        <item>
            <title>1.1.4</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fix "Show Dock icon" toggle not working: Dock icon was not appearing when enabled, and toggling off caused the window to disappear</li>
<li>Prevent app from terminating unexpectedly when all windows are closed</li>
<li>Fix window target defaulting to Tiley itself when launched by double-clicking the app; now correctly targets the previously active app's window</li>
<li>Fix main window appearing on login-item launch: the window no longer opens when the app is auto-launched as a login item at system startup</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
